keyFacts: The FBI's Human Trafficking/Victim-Centered Approach unit in New York was actively contacting potential Epstein victims in late July 2019.
A specific woman, described as a potential victim, was contacted on or around July 26, 2019.
The email indicates coordination and information sharing within law enforcement regarding victim outreach.
